<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dawn Neural | Vision</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #0a0a0c; 
            color: #e0e0e0; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            min-height: 100vh; 
        }
        nav { 
            background: #16161a; 
            padding: 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333; 
        }
        nav a { 
            color: #00bfff; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            margin: 0 20px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover { color: #ff8c00; }
        
        .content { 
            max-width: 900px; 
            margin: 50px auto; 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 20px; 
            flex: 1; 
        }
        h2 { font-size: 2.8rem; color: #00bfff; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #bbb; text-align: justify; }
        .highlight { color: #ff8c00; font-weight: bold; }
        
        /* עיצוב התמונה של המשרדים */
        .office-img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 850px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.15);
            margin: 40px auto 10px auto;
            display: block;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .office-img:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3);
            border-color: #ff8c00;
        }
        
        /* עיצוב הכיתוב של ג'מיני */
        .caption {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        footer { 
            background: #000; 
            color: #555; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-top: 1px solid #222; 
            margin-top: auto; 
        }
        footer a { color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="about.html">About</a>
        <a href="vision.html">Vision</a>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>At <span class="highlight">Dawn Neural</span>, we are architecting the future of human-AI collaboration. Our mission is to democratize high-level AI research and build the infrastructure for the next generation of digital intelligence.</p>
        
        <img src="dawn-hq.png" alt="Dawn Neural Headquarters Concept" class="office-img">
        <div class="caption">HQ Concept simulation generated by Gemini</div>

        <p>From our conceptualized <span class="highlight">Geodesic Dome Headquarters</span> to the deep underground server rooms, we believe in a world where technology and nature coexist through elegant, efficient code.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 Dawn Neural. Connect with us on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHK3r62od3ekDYVW9MiGUig" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
